                          type="entry">βαλανεῖον</ref>
                  </xr>
               </cit>
            </etym>
            <note anchored="true">
               Pl. (not in GenR) acc. to 
      <bibl type="modern" default="false" status="draft">Krauss, LW II 159b-160a</bibl>. For Syr. <term xml:lang="syc">ܒܢܐ</term>
               <term xml:lang="fjb">bnʾ</term> see
      <bibl type="modern" default="false" status="draft">Sokoloff, SL 161a</bibl>.
   </note>
